---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="FAQ">
  <div class="container" style="padding: var(--spacing-6) 0;">
    
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <section>
      <h3>How quickly will I hear back after submitting an intake form?</h3>
      <p>We mandate a strict internal response time of 3 business days for all submitted forms.</p>
      <h3>Is my data secure?</h3>
      <p>Yes. All uploaded files and intake details are encrypted and stored in completely private storage, only accessible to verified staff members.</p>
      <h3>Where are you located?</h3>
      <p>We are physically located at 5858 Belair Rd, Baltimore, MD 21206.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
